                  "inline_data": null,
                  "text": "When planning your trip to Berlin, here's some useful information for you:\n\n### Current Weather in Berlin\n- **Temperature:** 22°C\n- **Condition:** Partly cloudy\n- **Humidity:** 65%\n- **Wind:** 12 km/h\n- **Forecast:** Mild weather with occasional clouds expected throughout the day.\n\n### Local Attractions in Berlin\n- **City Center:** Main downtown area with a rating of 4.2.\n- **Historical Museum:** Offers insights into local history and culture, rated 4.3.\n- **Central Park:** A beautiful public park, rated 4.1.\n- **Old Town:** Historic district with traditional architecture, rated 4.4.\n- **Local Market:** Traditional marketplace to explore local goods, rated 4.0.\n\n### Currency Exchange\n- **Exchange Rate:** 1 USD = 0.92 EUR\n\nFeel free to let me know if you need more information or any other help with your travel plans!",
