                  "inline_data": null,
                  "text": "If you're planning a trip to Berlin, here's some helpful information for you:\n\n### Current Weather in Berlin:\n- **Temperature:** 22°C\n- **Condition:** Partly cloudy\n- **Humidity:** 65%\n- **Wind:** 12 km/h\n- **Forecast:** Mild weather with occasional clouds expected throughout the day\n\n### Top Attractions in Berlin:\n1. **City Center**\n   - **Type:** Area\n   - **Rating:** 4.2\n   - **Description:** Main downtown area, with plenty of shops and restaurants.\n\n2. **Historical Museum**\n   - **Type:** Museum\n   - **Rating:** 4.3\n   - **Description:** Offers insightful exhibits on local history and culture.\n\n3. **Central Park**\n   - **Type:** Park\n   - **Rating:** 4.1\n   - **Description:** A lovely public park perfect for a relaxing stroll or picnic.\n\n4. **Old Town**\n   - **Type:** District\n   - **Rating:** 4.4\n   - **Description:** Explore the historic district with traditional architecture and charming streets.\n\n5. **Local Market**\n   - **Type:** Market\n   - **Rating:** 4.0\n   - **Description:** Experience a traditional local marketplace with various goods and foods.\n\nIf you need more information or assistance planning your trip to Berlin, feel free to ask!",
